Biographical Highlights

Hogan was born on 1955 in Framingham, Massachusetts.
He holds a BS in Civil Engineering from the Massachusetts Institute of Technology (1977) and an MBA from McCombs School of Business, University of Texas (1981). 
Other Boards and Organizations

Former Member, Minnesota Business Partnership
Former Member, Board of Trustees, American Public Media Group 
 





